job.body:
Total vacancies:458

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Tradesman Mate, JOA 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for matrics pass has been published by the Ministry of Defence for Tradesman Mate vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Tradesman Mate, from 16-07-2021, and till the last date. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Tradesman Mate in the Ministry of Defence, your 1oth class must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The Starting Date of Advertisement is 10 to 16-07-2021
  •  The last date for Receipt of Application is 21 Days from the date of Advertisement

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

Ministry of Defence Tradesman Mate Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

Detailed vacancies:

How to apply for Ministry of Defence Tradesman Mate, JOA Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Tradesman Mate. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of the Ministry of Defence and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Ministry of Defence 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
